  "3315720": {
    "name": "位面领主：海盗与低语",
    "steam_appid": 3315720,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315720/extras/81b4b368f274f2b580578dd8c26449a2.avif?t=1738483032\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《位面领主：海盗与低语》</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>带有章节式剧情和克苏鲁元素的探索冒险游戏</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一切冒险的开端，你穿越到异世界，获得了穿越位面的能力……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在永恒的海盗酒馆、旧神的神殿这两个场景中，努力探索真相，寻找回到现实的方法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你并不是孤独一人，在永恒的位面里你会遇到一些朋友或敌人，完成他们的委托或者打败敌人能加快你的穿越进度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >注意，这其中会发生很多异常的事情， 要时刻小心旧神的力量，不要让他们吞噬你…</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >融合了RPG角色扮演、探索解谜的冒险游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你需要在场景中探索，发现和收集隐藏物品，解开谜题，逃离或击败敌人，完成这一切后会抵达故事的结尾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >请留意场景里的每一个细节，事情的真相往往隐藏在不起眼的角落。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自由探索的场景，丰富的可交互内容，更有多结局等你探索……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>注意：本游戏部分内容靠音效推动，建议佩戴耳机以获得最佳体验。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏展示：<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315720/extras/3b64e7af3a9d8b0886bf5a3b68d05b2c.avif?t=1738483032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315720/extras_big/3b64e7af3a9d8b0886bf5a3b68d05b2c.avif?t=1738483032 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315720/extras/4eec8082092a06ada4044e77eef0c63d.avif?t=1738483032\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315720/extras_big/4eec8082092a06ada4044e77eef0c63d.avif?t=1738483032 width=800 height=450 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315720/extras/fb2dbb76d28b052ab1894af202b0fd36.avif?t=1738483032\" data-big-src=https://